      "id": "PopularPost278080",
      "post_content": "People really need to reread the oracle text.  \n  \n\"Whenever a Mountain is tapped for mana, its controller adds ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) to his or her mana pool (in addition to the mana the land produces).\"  \n  \nAdds red.  \nRed. Not \"Double the mana,\" RED. You get an extra ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) from [Stomping Grounds](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stomping Grounds) or [Taiga](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Taiga), not ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol).",
      "posted_by": "DoragonShinzui",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost278080\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">People really need to reread the oracle text.<br/><br/>\"Whenever a Mountain is tapped for mana, its controller adds <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> to his or her mana pool (in addition to the mana the land produces).\"<br/><br/>Adds red.<br/>Red. Not \"Double the mana,\" RED. You get an extra <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> from <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stomping Grounds\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stomping Grounds\">Stomping Grounds</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Taiga\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Taiga\">Taiga</a>, not <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '278080'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy79844\">DoragonShinzui</span>\r\n                                (10/24/2012 4:45:35 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class